op shop
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a charity shop selling donated goods cheaply.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: to be distinguished from a pre-loved clothes store, and other commercial second-hand shops.
